Package: spr-krun-runtime
Version: @VERSION@
Section: admin
Priority: optional
Architecture: arm64
Maintainer: SPR Networks <support@supernetworks.org>
Depends: libc6, libgcc-s1, libcap2, libjson-c5, libseccomp2, libsystemd0, iproute2, jq
Recommends: docker-ce | docker.io
Description: SPR KVM runtime for isolated plugins
 Patched libkrun and crun runtime used by SPR plugins that need a full Linux
 kernel. It bridges guest TAP networking into private Docker plugin networks
 and provides Unix-socket to virtio-vsock IPC without exposing plugin APIs over
 TCP or UDP.
